OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FAs a heatwave hits Yorkshire, the
OL,7,     Fpatient numbers rise with the
OL,8,     Ftemperature. Documentary series
OL,9,     Ffilmed inside Barnsley casualty
OL,10,     Fdepartment.
