OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FDoctors treat a non-verbal young
OL,7,     Fman in a life-threatening
OL,8,     Fneurological emergency, while a
OL,9,     Fmidwife with severe spinal pain is
OL,10,     Ffeared to have cauda equina
OL,11,     Fsyndrome after back surgery.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FA butcher from Somerset brings a
OL,14,     Fmeaty lipoma on his neck for Dr
OL,15,     FDev Shah. Dr Toby Nelson has a
OL,16,     Fpatient with a skin condition
OL,17,     Faround her eyes.
